DiscArch Project
Overview
DiscArch is a C# project that automates the translation of software requirements into architectural decisions. It leverages GPT-4 for parsing requirements and an ILP-based optimizer for decision-making.

Components
RequirementParser: Parses natural language requirements into structured ASRs.
Architect: Generates architectural policies based on the parsed ASRs.
Usage
Clone the repository.
Install required dependencies.
Run CategorizedReqsExperiment with desired system settings.
View output in designated reporting format.
Contributing
Contributions are welcome. Please read the contributing guide for guidelines.
